exampleMethod(bytes[]).notice: This method is an example of how to interact with the Pyth contract. Fetch the priceUpdate from Hermes and pass it to the Pyth contract to update the prices. See https://docs.pyth.network/price-feeds/fetch-price-updates for more information on how to fetch the priceUpdate.
